  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Claude just got access to your Google Drive, Gmail, Slack, and GitHub.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ea4d325da9ae777cd89527db9c65f0f66e682c412a601d4168f5dd09d3306e5a",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "And most people have no idea this feature even exists.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ca21ebdeb65b8a9708bb28408810627240cafd95e57b3f34e2c027e75a1854ad",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 12
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "It's called Connectors. And the people who found it first are already months ahead of everyone else.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0dc75af5480bcb769170d3ac82c1f9f114a1caf923c39066190d63d35a4835e3",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 5.758548752834467,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 22
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Here's exactly what changed.\n\nConnector number one: Google Drive.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4b3056222fca0122c42abbdefbb699af1d48575b292cfdc019cbc55fedef8cea",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 39
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Claude can now read your actual docs. Not a copy you pasted in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d2443c4404bc9aab5f0c45668b9e08bee5d23883fb49158f56dfd71ed0b03abd",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 48
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Your real files, indexed and searchable inside the chat.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9bec30b9f904b8e0f5832a66de7651247ecb7ae8b59ebc1d5a84d8f5518b3e51",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 61
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Ask Claude to find that strategy doc from last March, and it finds it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b634cbdb6367da3a1a22da91ffd0620023d042936a81995afe55b011379b81c8",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 70
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Connector number two: Gmail. Claude reads your inbox and synthesizes it like a skilled assistant would.",
      "checksum": "sha256:de1609284551477d1745ac5fdab29c93ff05f4fc454ffdc9cf27b69bf377b1f8",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 7.151746031746032,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 84
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Point it at a thread and it drafts a reply in your voice, extracts action items, and flags anything urgent before your next meeting.",
      "checksum": "sha256:433d36a1ba472b76e487d532b567f919b6bdd331aa877db2c1fdf1b4d180cf1e",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 8.17342403628118,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 100
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Connector number three: Slack. Launched in January 2026 for Claude Pro and Max subscribers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c33fbe8bcb3a5f58f925527910fe34462bd97a685fd024f9bc4e60ca9fc1320f",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 6.130068027210885,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 124
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Claude searches your workspace channels, messages, and files during any conversation.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1f9b43a7478e453a32e294245d748661b16b36d00abc4509fcb35cbbefe00d24",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 138
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Your company's entire institutional knowledge, available on demand.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f5e7c3c05cc13d7ad04871c514b1440e7330aa46e913d428e4e01896ce6cdf3f",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 149
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Connector number four: GitHub. Claude can read your repositories, review pull requests, leave inline comments, and check for security patterns.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6ae2806d4fca678be2e31ddba1ba943dc7cd2c4d6179a6beeae29a0a49a3861e",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 8.916462585034013,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 157
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "The same review checklist you'd walk through manually, automated.\n\nThis is all built on Anthropic's open Model Context Protocol \u2014 MCP.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cc2af70fba27336a10c1296e76a00c3c0cbec45dbfbc12732e07051db4ca7bbb",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 8.126984126984127,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 177
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "And it's available right now on all plans, including the Free plan.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5076181c40c46df4681794216f140b8ec3ff9d06d8fbbcd3a7a2ae0723e09ffc",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 198
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "To enable it: click the plus icon in your chat, select Connectors, and choose a service.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0373b437aac6f86d952e47566ec74b32a752786e16c9671d44bf019dbc9bba6b",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 210
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Claude will ask for OAuth authorization.",
      "checksum": "sha256:216d00ea0dbcd13a958d19edc3972ebbbb7df9f7b06abe1673d774cf4e66b436",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 226
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "You control exactly what it can access. The people ignoring this are still copying and pasting files into Claude like it's 2024.",
      "checksum": "sha256:10aac9eb99191cfaef3eb3d436c9be97aa7ebb55c5b656adb5d805e4cb30c532",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 7.291065759637188,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 232
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "If you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous.ai community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:02fb55ac5d74a885fc367b08071566f2daf12f24bfd8b7bbc8b254c0367f19e3",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 254
    }
  ]
}